                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-09-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">新出土材料运用极多，摆脱了传统史观的束缚</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="805116743">
